			<td colspan="6" class="DetailTitle" style="text-align:center;">
                            Summary on Grant Application Form</td>
		</tr>
		<tr>
			<td colspan="6" class="DetailValue" style="padding:5px;">
                        <span id="lblAbstract">To create and exploit an 'environment' for building open, highly configurable, multi-purpose shop and cell control systems, this comprising a library of function modules and a set of open systems build and runtime support tools.  The purpose of the environment will be to structure and enable life-cycle processes associated with a new generation of controllers. Also during the project the environment will be used to build cell controllers and to evaluate their use at a user manufacturing site.</span>
                        </td>
		</tr>
